act.article:
2 Definitions. -

1 In these rules, unless the context 
otherwise requires,- 

 a "Act" means the Energy Conservation Act, 2001; 
 b "Form" means the forms specified under rule 3; 
 c "year" means the financial year beginning on the 1st day of April and 
  ending on the 31st March following; 
 d words and expression used herein and not defined, but defined in the 
  Act shall have the meanings assigned to them in the Act.
